Dear Alumni,

Countrywide Home Loans in Calabasas, CA is searching for a 
Compliance Manager.  Interested candidates can contact Ari 
Qutami at the information listed below job description.  
Please note that they are requesting salary history to be 
included with resume.

Thank you.


